the feed json file was created with AI (chatgpt 5.5) with sample data :)

started working on hero page and got carried away with the sign up too, after completing log and and sign up
moved to feed page asked chatgpt to make a json file with data( later had to redo it and be more speifec with the json) 
started first in hero page with the js file to get the data into an array
idea of the code is functions for each action


in html added for each catagorey a div with a id of that catagorey for simple sorting


starting with addEventListener that actives when the html Loades and the even does as following 
calls for fetchFeed()

collects all the catagories from the feed html file and insert them to an array

get what is in the searc field 

get's the current letter in the A-Z filter

diply all the data with the given parametrs ( a-z filler , search field)
if both are null (a-z at all search is empty) everything will be displyed
other wised the function function renderFeed(data)

will diply according to the filter parametrs


async function fetchFeed()
get's the data from the json file

function getPostsForSection(divId, feedData)
a router that calls the renderFeed function with the data that is needed for the given divId (catagorey)

function createAlphabetButtons()
creates the buttons for the A-Z filter and adds event listeners to them to call the renderFeed function with the given letter as a parameter

function formatStoppedWatchingAt(stoppedWatchingAt) 
i told chatgpt to use the format 0:0 if not watched
and x,x to represnt epsode and sesion and xx:xx for time left in the episode
this function transforms the data into the code


function createCard(item)
creates the card for each item in the feed with the data from the json file and the format of the card

function displayFeed(divId, feedData)
the function that actually displays the data in the given divId with the given feedData (after filtering it with the search field and the A-Z filter)
